ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"碗仔翅都係啦<br />\n<br />\n平民食唔起咪搵野過下癮囉"},{"pid":"7729b962c03ece71fd6053210daab4f9da24fe3a","tid":46244,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"但蟹柳好食過蟹"},{"pid":"fbcb34de87e852c8d75cd7298c58a6603a4a0449","tid":46244,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c05efcb3596ad0f4f338e2b194020cc217d59e","tid":46244,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你確定係魚肉黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係魚肉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n粉黎架咋</blockquote><br />\n秒殺"},{"pid":"c900c2070dd6e980245426ce510fca6ec90ed9c7","tid":46244,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係魚肉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n粉黎架咋</blockquote><br />\n秒殺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n　　很多人都知道蟹柳不是用真正蟹肉製成，包裝蟹柳上已列明成分：魚肉、水、小麥澱粉、色素、天然蟹味粉、防腐劑及添加劑等，並無蟹肉。「兩至三條蟹柳約有一肉的蛋白質，由於其成分也包括麵粉，多吃易令血糖提升；蟹柳亦不如肉類所含的蛋白質般豐富，故不能用來取代肉類，而且加工食品加入了很多色素，不宜多吃，即使進食亦應避免同時吃多於一種的加工食品，如紅腸、火腿及魚蛋等。」營養師鄭雅新說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n秒你個頭就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bcf385072074a6b649659f743ef583edbc14f1","tid":46244,"uid":45192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚肉冒充蟹肉<br />\n都冇解o既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗夠無狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9041b05b28738402ad1c587fe8f2b0ba42d9c940","tid":46244,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"